description: This file contains a database seed script that populates initial data into various tables such as users, profiles, posts, followers, reactions, and analytics in a social media database. It sets up sample users, their profiles, posts, social relationships, reactions to posts, and some analytics data.
external_files: None explicitly referenced as external files; only standard database cursor and connection methods are used

methods.name: run(conn)
methods.description: Main function that populates the database with seed data for users, profiles, posts, followers, reactions, and analytics.
